statements: SELECT * FROM machine_learning_models;

SELECT model_id, model_name, model_type, model_path FROM machine_learning_models WHERE model_type = 'classification';

SELECT deployment_id, model_name, deployment_status FROM model_deployments ORDER BY deployment_id DESC;

SELECT model_name, deployment_status, user_feedback FROM MachineLearningModels JOIN ModelDeployments ON MachineLearningModels.model_id = ModelDeployments.model_id JOIN UserPredictions ON ModelDeployments.deployment_id = UserPredictions.prediction_id WHERE UserPredictions.user_rating > 3;
